data.description: Escape to your own backyard with views of this one acre pond surrounded by palm trees. Tremendous 40x100ft barndominium with attached 50x100ft workshop and detached carport, featuring a large covered patio with total privacy. Automatic doors throughout home.  All 3 bedrooms have a full bath. Inside you will love the large living room, eat-in kitchen with built-in cabinets and spacious master suite. Sewing/hobby room with countertops and cabinets. Combination office with workbench in addition to full office attached to a commercial kitchen with wine racks. Large den with patio access.    More acreage available. Existing CAN#02660000000101 for entire property.
